# Platform Core — очередь агентов (planner)

When `dev:core` is running on `:3001`, agents **must** pull work from the live planner queue (not ad-hoc scope).

## API (development only)

| Method | Path | Action |
|--------|------|--------|
| GET | `/api/dev/platform-core/planner` | Full snapshot + statuses |
| GET | `/api/dev/platform-core/planner/next` | Next open task (P0 first) |
| POST | `/api/dev/platform-core/planner/claim` | `{ "by": "cursor-agent", "id?": "..." }` → in_progress |
| POST | `/api/dev/platform-core/planner/run-agents` | Claim + dispatch prompt → `.planning/platform-core-agent-dispatch.json` |
| POST | `/api/dev/platform-core/planner/analyze` | Honest scan → up to 10 new items (dev + tech-debt) |
| POST | `/api/dev/platform-core/planner/complete` | `{ "id": "...", "by": "...", "note?": "..." }` → done |

Runtime state: `_ai-share/synth-1-full/.planning/platform-core-planner-runtime.json`

## Agent workflow

1. Ensure `npm run dev:core` / SYNTHA is up (`GET /api/dev/syntha-status`).
2. `GET .../planner/next` or `POST .../planner/claim` with `"by": "cursor-agent"`.
3. Implement **only** the claimed task in canonical paths (`_ai-share/synth-1-full`, FastAPI in `app/`).
4. Verify (lint / smoke for touched area).
5. `POST .../planner/complete` with task `id` and short `note`.
6. Repeat while user session is active and `open` count &gt; 0.

## UI

Hub `/platform` → tab **План** — polls every 5s; **Агенты · online** when API reachable.

**UI buttons:**
- **▶ Запустить агентов (чат)** — claim + **Cursor SDK local agent** + live chat panel (poll `/api/dev/platform-core/planner/session/{id}`)
- Requires: `npm run planner:agent:install` + `CURSOR_API_KEY` in `.env.local` (cursor.com/dashboard/integrations)
- **🔍 Проанализировать (+10)** — section audit gaps + code TODO/stub scan (no LLM hype)
- Per-row **▶ Агентам** — claim that task + open chat

## CLI (from monorepo root)

```bash
npm run planner:next
npm run planner:claim
npm run planner:complete -- <task-id> "note"
```

## Adding manual items

Edit `src/lib/platform-core-planner-agent.ts` → `PLATFORM_CORE_PLANNER_AGENT_ITEMS`.
